Feature: The module can switch between virtual cassettes

  Scenario: After initiating controls from a save, it uses saved cassette selection

  Scenario: Turning the knob first initiates backup of the current cassette, then it loads the new one, and then it starts playing from it

  Scenario: Turning the knob while it is loading a previously stored recording immediatelly starts loading a the newly selected cassette

  Scenario: Changing cassette also recovers the effects that were used with it

  Scenario: After a cassette is selected, the display shows how much space of SD it occupies, and it is newer less than a single LED
